512
00:49:04,261 --> 00:49:06,663
We're having dinner, Mr. Public.

513
00:49:06,763 --> 00:49:09,199
No, I said I was having dinner with my wife.

514
00:49:09,299 --> 00:49:12,274
I found this picture in a magazine.

515
00:49:12,402 --> 00:49:16,567
One word from me,
