516
00:49:17,174 --> 00:49:18,876
What do you feel like eating?

517
00:49:18,976 --> 00:49:22,346
Virgil Starkwell becomes the victim
of a blackmail plot.

518
00:49:22,446 --> 00:49:25,082
Miss Blair, confident of her power
to expose him...

519
00:49:25,182 --> 00:49:27,951
...begins making small demands for money.

520
00:49:28,051 --> 00:49:30,686
