583
00:54:44,968 --> 00:54:47,937
I'm gonna rob a bank.

584
00:54:48,505 --> 00:54:50,505
No, Virgil, not again.

585
00:54:50,540 --> 00:54:52,309
Yes, I think so.

586
00:54:52,409 --> 00:54:55,345
I think that our only way out of this mess
is for me to...

587
00:54:55,445 --> 00:54:58,048
There's a little dinky bank in Ross County...

588
00:54:58,148 --> 00:55:00,350
...and I think if I can get
two or three good men...

589
00:55:00,450 --> 00:55:01,751
I can get in there and get it...

590
00:55:01,851 --> 00:55:06,441
...and we could go down to Mexico
or up to Canada or...

591
00:55:07,023 --> 00:55:11,094
