594
00:55:27,110 --> 00:55:29,110
Don't turn around.

595
00:55:30,046 --> 00:55:34,211
I wanna speak to you
about a business proposition.

596
00:55:38,121 --> 00:55:40,121
It's a bank job.

597
00:55:41,224 --> 00:55:43,627
Couple of guys and myself
are gonna get together...

598
00:55:43,727 --> 00:55:47,097
