Quarter of a million dollars.

599
00:55:47,197 --> 00:55:49,666
We walk in and take it like that.

600
00:55:49,766 --> 00:55:53,251
It's an easy job. See, we just pull up...

601
00:55:53,703 --> 00:55:55,703
...take it.

602
00:56:01,511 --> 00:56:04,446
How long have you been...

603
00:56:04,514 --> 00:56:07,829
Because I said the part about the bank.

604
00:56:11,855 --> 00:56:14,745
You guys are dressing alike again.

605
00:56:18,428 --> 00:56:20,428
I broke it myself.

606
00:56:20,997 --> 00:56:24,034
All the boys in the neighborhood
went wrong. It wasn't his fault.

607
00:56:24,134 --> 00:56:26,536
We didn't have time for him.
We were working.

608
00:56:26,636 --> 00:56:28,471
Would you like to see my stamp collection?

609
00:56:28,571 --> 00:56:31,975
What do you mean?
- I have a collection of stamps.

610
00:56:32,075 --> 00:56:35,220
First he selects an appropriate bank.

611
00:56:35,512 --> 00:56:38,381
Next, he cases the bank
by cleverly concealing a camera...

