649
00:59:08,230 --> 00:59:12,650
The fools in Hollywood,
they didn't recognize genius.

650
00:59:14,002 --> 00:59:18,807
But now, I shall wear the uniform
of a director once again.

651
00:59:18,907 --> 00:59:21,899
And you will be my actor.

652
00:59:22,477 --> 00:59:26,682
You will enter the bank and say,
'Up with your hands, this is a stickup.'

653
00:59:26,782 --> 00:59:31,446
Thereby announcing our theme:
Men's greed.

654
00:59:31,820 --> 00:59:34,423
Now say it. Let me hear the line.

655
00:59:34,523 --> 00:59:40,388
Up with your hands, this is a stickup.
- No. More feeling. Again, now.

656
00:59:40,762 --> 00:59:45,290
This is a bank robbery, not a movie.
- Yes, of course.

657
00:59:45,601 --> 00:59:47,601
Forgive me.

658
00:59:47,636 --> 00:59:51,801
I will be fine when the time comes.
Thank you all.

659
00:59:52,140 --> 00:59:54,140
Everybody, take five.

660
