I washed it last night.

671
01:00:48,697 --> 01:00:50,766
Why did you wash it?
I was gonna wear it today.

672
01:00:50,866 --> 01:00:52,401
I washed it because it was dirty.

673
01:00:52,501 --> 01:00:54,169
