697
01:02:54,623 --> 01:02:57,148
You call this a bank robbery?

698
01:02:57,492 --> 01:03:01,588
I yelled 'action' five minutes ago.

699
01:03:02,597 --> 01:03:05,402
Is this the way to pick up money?

700
01:03:08,336 --> 01:03:10,906
What's going on here?
There's a million cops outside.

701
01:03:11,006 --> 01:03:13,006
Let's get out of here.

702
01:03:30,258 --> 01:03:33,929
Each member of the gang
gets five years for his part in the crime.

703
01:03:34,029 --> 01:03:36,029
Virgil gets ten.

704
01:03:36,098 --> 01:03:39,735
He is taken, not to prison this time,
but to a road gang...

705
01:03:39,835 --> 01:03:43,939
...where his criminal behavior
