706
01:03:44,039 --> 01:03:48,119
You men come here
because you committed crimes...

707
01:03:48,143 --> 01:03:51,480
...rendering you unfit to
live in decent society.

708
01:03:51,580 --> 01:03:53,181
That's too bad.

709
01:03:53,281 --> 01:03:58,186
I think you're gonna find
you made a mistake you're gonna regret.

710
01:03:58,286 --> 01:04:02,991
Our job, mine and the boys, is to see
